Nighttime Stories (1991) [VHSRip]

The premise of this tape is right on: somebody really needs to write a few hot fairytales that lovers can read to each other at bedtime to help one partner or another get in the mood. Unfortunately, what's presented here is a rather tepid batch. Melanie Moore is delightfully explicit in the first story, &quot;Hot Nipples&quot;, but the girl/girl/girler that follows needs some oomph! Somewhat more entertaining is the threesome with Debi Diamond, Moore and Blake Palmer, as the ladies practically sandwich Palmer between them. Story #4, &quot;Unchained Melanie&quot;, for some reason stars Sharise, who nicely straddles partner Steve Drake. And of course, the final coupling between Spears and Rogers should leave you with a satisfied smile on your face. Director Marino is apparently a protegÃƒÂ© of, in this case, producer Scotty Fox, and it shows.

